MESSAGE.value: ANDROIDPLOT-56 Restructured project to place all sample apps under the Examples/ subdirectory.
ANDROIDPLOT-56 Created parent/child mvn pom structure. Created pom for Examples.
ANDROIDPLOT-56 Added support for building native android projects from mvn.
ANDROIDPLOT-56 Examples now fire off of Examples/pom.xml compile and clean maven targets.
ANDROIDPLOT-56 Setup parent pom to recursively build all sub modules.
ANDROIDPLOT-50 Minor fixes here and there
ANDROIDPLOT-50 Removing dynamically generated directories from svn.
ANDROIDPLOT-55 Removing dynamically generated directories from vcs.
ANDROIDPLOT-68 Implemented tabular legend functionality for LegendWidget.
ANDROIDPLOT-68 Modified LegendWidge's implementation of TableModel to leverage SizeLayout for calculating icon sizes in absolute or relative values.
ANDROIDPLOT-61 Created a rudimentary time series sample project.
ANDROIDPLOT-61 Fixed plot title.
ANDROIDPLOT-68 Abstracted TableModel and created Dynamic and Fixed implementations.
ANDROIDPLOT-73 First pass at implementing touch support.
ANDROIDPLOT-73 Added cursor label and background
ANDROIDPLOT-73 Fixed a couple bugs that came up while answering the question here: http://androidplot.com/forum/index.php/topic,35.msg116.html#msg116
ANDROIDPLOT-75 - Moved line/label drawing code into two private methods; one for domain and the other for range.
ANDROIDPLOT-77 - Added copy/style change logic.
ANDROIDPLOT-27 - Created ValueMarker classes and added list logic to XYPlot to manage markers.
ANDROIDPLOT-27 - Finished XValueMarker and YValueMarker and added rendering code to XYGraphWidget.

ANDROIDPLOT-74 Added a check on addSeries to make sure an existing renderer instance is not already available for use before creating a new one, as these renderers become cached during the life of a plot.
ANDROIDPLOT-27 - Development on marker support is completed. (for now)
ANDROIDPLOT-72 - proguard and javadoc:jar are now called as part of the package directive in androidplot-core.

ANDROIDPLOT-72 - Added the obfuscuted subdir in the androidplot-core target artifact dir to separate it from the base jar. Having them in a single directory was causing issues with example ant projects picking up duplicate class definitions.
